<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Open_source_hardware&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Machines and tools">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Machines and tools</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>The <a href="/wiki/Multimachine" title="Multimachine">Multimachine</a>, an open source <a href="/wiki/Machine_tool" title="Machine tool">machine tool</a> project</li>
</ul>
