<p><a name="Home_automation" id="Home_automation"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Open_source_hardware&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: Home automation">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Home automation</span></h2>
<p>A range of open design hardware can be used in <a href="/wiki/Home_automation" title="Home automation">home automation</a>. <sup id="cite_ref-19" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-19" title=""><span>[</span>20<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-20" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-20" title=""><span>[</span>21<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
