<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Open_source_hardware&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Other projects">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Other projects</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/RONJA" title="RONJA">RONJA</a> - Open source Free Space Optic system, DIY in a garage, 10 Mbit/s full duplex/1.4 km</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/LED_Throwies" title="LED Throwies" class="mw-redirect">LED Throwies</a> - non-destructive graffiti and light displays.</li>
